These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, pop
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of pop##1
2. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of pop##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | pop | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
2. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | rabbit | fish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, bus
1. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | bike | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |
| Hobby   | puzzles | magic-tricks |

 #################################

 
